Name: Plaid Chain Flares
Short description: Clueless meets Daria. High-waisted 90s-inspired plaid pants with a flared bottom hem, zip fly, front and back pockets, and attached chain belt.

Name: Classic Long Sleeve Tee
Short description: Hey, smooth talker. This tee will have you feeling clean and classy like a Cadillac. 100% Heavyweight Cotton.

Name: OJ Hoodie
Short description: Is there anything better than a freshly squeezed glass of OJ? Didn’t think so. Show your support for this long loved juice. Classic Alter Ego Heavyweight Fit.

Name: Nirvana Long Sleeve Tee
Short description: I wanted to be in a punk band before I even heard any punk music. Our striped Nirvana tee is unisex, featuring an oversized and slightly boxy fit.

Name: VHS Hoodie
Short description: *hits rewind on life, goes back to sleep* Unisex hoodie with motif of ancient technology, drawstring hood, and kangaroo-style front pocket.

Name: Dolphin Tee
Short description: Dolphins sometimes swim with in a crew of 1000 and more. You too can roll deep in this soft n’ faded periwinkle crewneck with print on front.

Name: Racer Long Sleeve Tee
Short description: Skr skr. Long sleeve tee with faded graphic on the chest and back. Illegally soft midweight cotton, probably the softest most comfortable tee you'll ever wear.

Name: Lovely Tee
Short description: Isn’t she lovely? This cutie tee is soft, prewashed lightweight cotton that will grace your skin like freshly scented powder, summer breeze…all that jazz.

Name: Logo Striped Long Sleeve Tee
Short description: Alter Ego captures the spirit of London punk, East Coast hip hop and 90s nostalgia. Enjoy the ride in this unisex oversized tee. Made in the USA.

Name: Youth and Love Tee
Short description: Summer breeze, long drives, a full sky of stars. Remember whatever you dreamed of when you were young and wide-eyed in this soft pre-washed crewneck tee.

Name: Super Soft Pants
Short description: How can you know what you’re missing when you’ve never had pants as soft as these in your life? Made of pillowy soft Supima Cotton, you’ll never change again.

Name: Basic Straightleg Denim
Short description: Things don’t always need to be so complicated. Sturdy-yet-soft denim so you can do all your favorite things: play with dogs and eat food. 32” inseam.

Name: Meteor Runner Sneaker
Short description: Run to the galaxy and back in these trendy chunky gel-lined sneaks. Well okay, they’re mostly for showing up — stuntin’ on em is the journey. US Women sizes.

Name: Disruption Sneaker
Short description: Nothing beats a fresh pair of lace up, padded for comfort chunky sole sneakers. Pull tabs help make getting on them a little easier.

Name: Luna Boot
Short description: White lace up combat boots with punk-inspired details, air-cushioned sole, metal eyelets and a slightly raised heel.

Name: Finish Line Slides
Short description: Get a head start on summer in these fun, check patterned slides. Waterproof and lightweight, you’ll lap everyone in sight.

Name: Pink Cosmo Sunglasses
Short description: Kirakira lovers, it’s your time to shine. Translucent pink sunglasses with sparkly baby pink tinted shades.

Name: Scarlet Lady Sunglasses
Short description: Meow! Red acrylic 90s-inspired shades with tinted lenses. Warning: extreme cat eye frame may result in fire looks.

Name: Tommy Hat
Short description: Plaid bucket cap inspired by Tommy Boy Records, the rap label that released RuPaul’s dance/house album Supermodel of The World in 1993.

Name: Shout Out Beanie
Short description: Where my queens at? Thick rib knit with an XL contrast pom, this hat has your back in all types of weather.

Name: Alter Ego Sticker Pack
Short description: One for you, one for me… High quality vinyl Alter Ego stickers for anywhere and everywhere. Sharing is cool.
